    cito:cites <http://taxon-concept.plazi.org/id/Animalia/Leuceruthrus_stephanocauda_Faust_1921>, <http://taxon-concept.plazi.org/id/Animalia/Leuceruthrus_ocalana_Smith_1935>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7753945> ;
    dc:creator "Bullard, Matthew R. Womble and Stephen A." ;
    dc:title "Leuceruthrus Marshall and Gilbert 1905" ;
    trt:augmentsTaxonConcept <http://taxon-concept.plazi.org/id/Animalia/Leuceruthrus_Gilbert_1905> ;
    trt:publishedIn <http://dx.doi.org/10.1645/22-36> ;
    a trt:Treatment .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.1645/22-36>
    bibo:endPage "394" ;
    bibo:issue "4" ;
    bibo:journal "Journal of Parasitology" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2022-08-18" ;
    bibo:startPage "374" ;
    bibo:volume "108" ;
    dc:creator "Bullard, Matthew R. Womble and Stephen A." ;
    dc:date "2022" ;
    dc:title "Azygiid Parasites Of North American Endemic Pleurocerids And Centrarchids: Revision Of Leuceruthrus Marshall And Gilbert, 1905 (Digenea: Azygiidae), Description Of Two New Species, And Phylogenetic Analysis" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7753945> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7753945>
    dc:description "Figures 1, 2. (1) Adult of Leucer- uthrus micropteri Marshall and Gil- bert, 1905 from largemouth bass, Micropterus salmoides from Wheeler Reservoir, Alabama (USNM 1593581) showing mouth (m), oral sucker (os), pharynx (p), ceca (c) near origin, prostatic sac (ps), genital atrium (ga), genital pore (gp), ventral sucker (vs), distal end of uterus (ud), testes (t), vitellarium (vi), uterus origin (uo) near ovary (o), vitelline reservoir (vr), con- fluence of excretory ducts (ed), excre- tory bladder (eb), and excretory pore (ep). Ventral view. (2) Terminal male genitalia of L. micropteri (USNM 1593581) showing comparable features as illustrated in Fig. 1 plus seminal vesicle (sv), pars prostatica (pp), me- traterm (mt), and hermaphroditic pore (hp). Ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7753945/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

